<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>
    <%= title %>
  </title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1,
    h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <h1>
    <%= title %>
  </h1>

  <p>Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US') %>
  </p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We collect the following information from users:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Personal information such as name, email address, phone number</li>
    <li>Login information and activity on the application</li>
    <li>Device and browser information</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
  <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
    <li>Communicate with users</li>
    <li>Conduct analysis and research</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Information Security</h2>
  <p>We are committed to protecting users' personal information through appropriate security measures.</p>

  <h2>4. Information Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not share personal information with third parties unless required by law or with user consent.</p>

  <h2>5. User Rights</h2>
  <p>Users have the right to access, modify, or delete their personal information.</p>

  <h2>6. Policy Changes</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Please check regularly for the latest information.</p>

  <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please contact us at: [contact email address]</p>
</body>

</html>